<% content_for :title do %>Privacy Policy | <%= installation_brand_name %><% end %>

<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="updated">Last updated: June 27, 2026</p>

<p>
  <%= installation_brand_name %> (“Converra”, “we”, “us”) is operated by <strong>SamaBrains Solutions</strong>.
  This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our customer support platform at
  <a href="<%= legal_site_url %>"><%= legal_site_url.sub(%r{^https?://}, '') %></a>.
</p>

<h2>1. Who this applies to</h2>
<p>This policy applies to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Businesses and their agents who create accounts and use Converra</li>
  <li>End customers who contact those businesses through connected channels (e.g. website chat, email, Facebook Messenger)</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. Information we collect</h2>
<p><strong>Account holders (agents and admins)</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Name, email address, company name, and password (stored securely)</li>
  <li>Workspace settings, team membership, and usage within the platform</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Customer conversations</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Messages, contact details, and attachments sent through channels you connect</li>
  <li>Channel metadata (e.g. Facebook Page ID, Messenger sender profile) when you enable integrations</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Technical data</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>IP address, browser type, device information, and logs for security and reliability</li>
  <li>Cookies and session data required to keep you signed in</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. How we use information</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Provide, operate, and improve the Converra service</li>
  <li>Route conversations to the correct workspace and agents</li>
  <li>Send transactional emails (e.g. invitations, password resets, notifications) via our email provider</li>
  <li>Connect to third-party channels you authorize (e.g. Meta/Facebook Messenger)</li>
  <li>Protect against abuse, fraud, and security incidents</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Third-party services</h2>
<p>When you connect integrations, data may be processed by those providers under their own policies, including:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Meta (Facebook Messenger)</strong> — when you connect a Facebook Page</li>
  <li><strong>Email delivery (Brevo)</strong> — for system and notification emails</li>
  <li><strong>Hosting (Railway)</strong> — application and database infrastructure</li>
</ul>
<p>We only share data with third parties as needed to deliver features you enable.</p>

<h2>5. Data retention</h2>
<p>
  Conversation and account data is retained while your workspace is active and as needed for legitimate business
  purposes. Workspace admins may delete conversations and contacts within the product. You may request account
  deletion by contacting us.
</p>

<h2>6. Your rights</h2>
<p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to access, correct, delete, or export your personal data. Contact us to make a request.</p>

<h2>7. Data deletion</h2>
<p>
  To request deletion of your Converra account and associated personal data, email
  <a href="mailto:info@samabrains.com">info@samabrains.com</a> from the address linked to your account.
  We will process verified requests within a reasonable timeframe.
</p>

<h2>8. Security</h2>
<p>
  We use industry-standard measures including encryption in transit (HTTPS), access controls, and secure
  infrastructure. No method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
</p>

<h2>9. Children</h2>
<p>Converra is a business service not directed at children under 16. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

<h2>10. Changes</h2>
<p>We may update this policy from time to time. The “Last updated” date at the top will reflect changes.</p>

<h2>11. Contact</h2>
<p>
  <strong>SamaBrains Solutions</strong><br>
  Email: <a href="mailto:info@samabrains.com">info@samabrains.com</a><br>
  Website: <a href="<%= legal_site_url %>"><%= legal_site_url %></a>
</p>

